---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Sirsandwich Shop" description="Learn about Sirsandwich Shop's story, our commitment to quality, and our passion for creating the perfect sandwich experience">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">About Sirsandwich Shop</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Discover our story, our values, and our commitment to crafting the perfect sandwich experience
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Our Story Section -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Founded in 2024, Sirsandwich Shop began with a simple mission: to elevate the humble sandwich 
          into an art form. What started as a passion project by sandwich enthusiasts has grown into 
          a beloved local destination for food lovers who appreciate quality and creativity.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Our founder, Sir Sandwich himself, spent years perfecting recipes and sourcing the finest 
          ingredients from local farmers and artisanal producers. Every sandwich tells a story of 
          craftsmanship, tradition, and innovation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Values Section -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">🌱 Fresh & Local</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We partner with local farms and suppliers to ensure our ingredients are always fresh, 
            sustainable, and support our community.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">👨‍🍳 Artisanal Craft</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Every sandwich is handcrafted with attention to detail, from our daily-baked bread 
            to our house-made condiments and dressings.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">🤝 Customer First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Your satisfaction is our priority. We listen to feedback and continuously improve 
            our offerings to exceed your expectations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">🌍 Sustainability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We're committed to environmentally friendly practices, from compostable packaging 
            to minimizing food waste.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
            👨‍🍳
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Sir Sandwich</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Founder & Head Chef</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
            Passionate about creating unique flavor combinations and perfecting classic recipes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
            👩‍💼
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Emma Johnson</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Operations Manager</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
            Ensures every order meets our high standards and customers leave happy.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
            👨‍🌾
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Marcus Green</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Sourcing Specialist</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
            Connects us with the best local farms and artisanal producers in the region.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Back to Home -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="/" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition duration-300">
        ← Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 